{"type": "article", "id": 9400, "title": "“Bonton” 耳环灯具", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-11T07:23:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235232rdhinVxFE1mtK5OC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t设计师 Cristina Celestino 受到耳环设计的启发，为意大利品牌 Torremato 设计了一款叫做 “Bonton” 的灯具，这款灯具系列的每一只灯上面都设计了一个蝶形旋钮，材料上选择的是铜，这些小旋钮和下面的吊灯配合在一起，看上去像是一个个形状各异的耳环。这个作品在米兰国际灯饰展进行了展出。这是<a href=\"http://www.torremato.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Torremato 的官方主页</a>，可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235230oX9VeFdDysxGiT0J.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235230BimdIoMUW390Rlh1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052352317X2QipfzGsmNnacR.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68948655\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235231PUjywg5TrXiuOJC7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70782396\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235231Dkr18x6Egqp2LCyB.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66870416\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}